@@ -5,6 +5,40 @@ All notable changes to this project are documented here.
 The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/),
 and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).
 
+## [0.2.3] - 2026-05-27
+
+PATCH. Bug fix + dev tooling on top of the 0.2.0 platform. Under `0.x`, only
+breaking changes increment the minor version; everything else is a patch.
+
+> Versioning note: this commit (`199409b`) consolidates the work previously
+> released as `0.2.1` (docs) and `0.2.2` (rank-drop fix) after a workspace
+> reset orphaned those tags. The `v0.2.1`/`v0.2.2` tags still exist on detached
+> commits, so this release increments past them to `0.2.3` rather than reusing
+> a burned version number.
+
+### Fixed
+
+- **Keyword table now surfaces lost rankings.** Rank *drops* were rendered with
+  the same `—` glyph as "no change," hiding declines from users. Drops now render
+  `↓ N` in `text-danger`; gains stay `↑ N` in `text-success`; flat stays `—`
+  (`src/features/rankings/components/KeywordTable.tsx`).
+
+### Added
+
+- Extracted pure `rankDelta()` / `formatRankDelta()` logic into
+  `src/features/rankings/rank.ts` (non-finite-safe: `NaN`/`Infinity` → flat/0).
+- `node --test` harness (`npm test` via `node --import tsx --test`) plus `tsx`
+  devDependency; unit tests for rank-delta and number formatting
+  (`rank.test.ts`, `src/lib/format.test.ts`).
+- Test-harness & pure-logic coverage ADR (`docs/adr/ADR-0001`), product backlog
+  brainstorm (Markdown + JSON), and the 2026-05-21 moonshots planning set.
+
+### Changed
+
+- `KeywordTable` refactored to consume the extracted `rank.ts` helpers.
+- README tech-stack refreshed to the 0.2.0 platform (Next.js 16 · React 19 ·
+  TypeScript 6 · Tailwind CSS 4 · ESLint 10).
+
