+
+## Implementation addendum — 2026-05-27 (IMPLEMENTED & GREEN)
+
+The plan above is now fully implemented against the current tree. (Note: a
+prior implementation was recorded but was **not present in the workspace at the
+start of this run** — `package.json` had no `test` script, `tsx` was absent, and
+`rank.ts`/`*.test.ts` did not exist. Re-implemented from the ADR.)
+
+Delivered:
+
+- **Task 1 — runner.** `tsx@^4.22.3` devDependency + `"test": "node --import tsx
+  --test \"src/**/*.test.ts\""`. Confirmed working on **Node v24.12.0**
+  (glob support resolved — the ≥22 UNVERIFIED note is now verified on v24).
+- **Task 2 — `src/lib/format.test.ts`** (19 tests): U+2212 minus asserted
+  explicitly (and asserted *not* to contain ASCII `-`), `-0`/`0` → `$0.00`,
+  half-expand rounding (`1.005 → $1.01`, `1234.5 → $1,235` at 0 decimals),
+  grouping on large values, NaN leak pinned.
+- **Task 3 — `src/features/rankings/rank.ts`** (`rankDelta` + `formatRankDelta`,
+  pure, non-finite-guarded). `KeywordTable.tsx` refactored to consume it.
+- **Task 4 — `src/features/rankings/rank.test.ts`** (9 tests) incl. a regression
+  guard that **drops never collapse to `—`**. Defect fixed: drops now render
+  `↓ N` in `text-danger`; improvements `↑ N` in `text-success`; flat `—`.
+- **Task 5 — NaN decision RESOLVED.** `format.ts` NaN behavior (`$NaN`/`NaN%`) is
+  **deliberately pinned, not guarded** — changing money/percent display needs
+  product input. New `rankDelta` **is** guarded (non-finite → `flat`/0).
+
+**Verification:** `npm test` → **28 pass / 0 fail** (~263 ms); `tsc --noEmit`
+clean. One UI-output change (rank drops now visible as `↓ N`) flagged for
+sign-off before production — no drop row exists in current mock data, so live
+output is unchanged today.
